item.title: Interview with Dwellicious - Organizing and Sharing Your Real Estate Bookmarks
item.description: A real estate searcher’s dream, Dwellicious allows it’s users to bookmark links from popular real estate sites and compare different features between them. Similar to other social bookmarking sites like Delicious, users can add tags to their bookmarks to separate their different properties into categories.
